title: RealWifeStories - Alektra Blue, Nina Elle (Swingers On Vacation
description:
Alektra was looking forward to a romantic weekend alone with her husband Michael, but Michael has other plans. He thought surprising his wife with a swingers resort would spice up the marriage! Alektra is shocked to find another couple in their hotel room, but maybe this is just the jolt her marriage needs.
